// "Antibiotics and Treatment Protocols" question bank (empiric treatment by
// infection site + definitive therapy by organism). Two brand-new topics cover
// question groups with no existing home (Skin/Soft Tissue/Bone/Joint infections,
// and Resistant Gram-Negative/MDR organism therapy); the rest are routed into
// existing Infectious Diseases topics via EXTRA_ID_QUIZ, mirroring the
// EXTRA_CARDIO_QUIZ/EXTRA_RHEUM_QUIZ/EXTRA_NEPHRO_QUIZ pattern.

